    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m selling my absolute gem of a car, and honestly, it\u2019s in such pristine, mint condition that you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh car smell. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make someone very happy. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
