      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six. This unit has undergone a comprehensive mechanical baseline, including a professional VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement to ensure reciprocating assembly longevity. The chassis integrity is bolstered by a structural subframe reinforcement, mitigating common floor pan fatigue. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. The suspension retains factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing exceptional lateral grip and steering feedback. This is a turn-key example with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
