    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade masterpiece that defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and shows like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, and has been treated with a multi-year ceramic coating for lasting protection. The wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, folder-organized service history showing preventative maintenance performed well ahead of manufacturer intervals. The engine bay is detailed to a show-standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its life of fair-weather use only. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved example for the most discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than the best.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
