    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to show you this absolute gem. This car has been my pride and joy, and honestly, it still looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty since day one\u2014it's spotless inside and out. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, you\u2019ve definitely found it! I'd love for you to come by and see it for yourself\u2014I promise you're going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
