    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system has been fully overhauled. The chassis remains true with factory-spec bushings and dampers, providing the precise feedback this platform is renowned for. The exterior finish is flawless, showing no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment, while the interior Nappa leather maintains its factory matte texture. A turn-key, analog masterpiece for the serious enthusiast.",
